/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, looking upwards towards the sky, giving a sense of scale and grandeur to the scene. The street is flanked by buildings on both sides, their facades adorned with various signs and advertisements, hinting at the commercial nature of the area. Cars and bicycles are parked along the sides of the street, adding to the urban atmosphere. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the backdrop of a hazy sky, a common sight in many cityscapes. The colors in the image are predominantly gray and brown, reflecting the overcast sky and the earthy tones of the buildings and streets. However, there are also splashes of green from the trees lining the street, providing a touch of nature amidst the concrete jungle.
